title: Centrally located Inner Sunset in-law studio on Judah St & Funston
posting_body: ['* *', '* AVAILABLE NOW for Immediate Move-In * * *', 'Highlights:', '- Walking distance to UCSF', '- Four blocks from 9th Ave corridor (lots of restaurants, shops, etc)', "- One block from Andronico's Supermarket & Irving Street", '- 2 blocks from Golden Gate Park', '- N-Judah bus stop right outside', '- Easy accessibility to Downtown SF', 'Description:', '- Great floor plan layout', '- Easy keyless entry & smart auto-lock', '- Kitchen includes dishwasher, full size gas stove and refrigerator, granite counter and plenty of cabinets with pull out shelves', '- Recessed lighting in kitchen and dimmable track lighting in room.', '- Full bath has tub and linen cabinet for storage', '- Independent entrance', '- Every room has a window', '- Plenty of street parking available (not 2-hr zoned so no need to pay for permits)', 'Notes:', '- Utilities not included', '- No smoking, no pets please', '- Minimum 1 year lease', '- Comfortably fit 2 occupants', '- Please bring earnings statements and any other documents to support your application', 'When replying, please provide an introduction about yourself.', 'Please include an email contact and phone number.', 'Credit report, income verification, and good references upon request.', 'Looking for clean, responsible tenants who want to treat the property like a home (as opposed to a "rental").', 'Available Now', 'Keywords: studio, inner sunset, in-law, 1 bedroom']
